column2: SELECT   G.ra, G.dec, S.mjd, S.plate, S.fiberID,       S.z, S.zErr, S.rChi2, S.velDisp, S.velDispErr,      G.extinction_r, G.psfMag_r, G.psfMagErr_r,   G.objID, GSI.specObjID,   p.psffwhm_u, p.psffwhm_g, p.psffwhm_r, p.psffwhm_i, p.psffwhm_z    INTO mydb.MyTable FROM photoprimary pp CROSS APPLY    GalSpecInfo GSI, PhotoObjAll p, SpecObj S, Galaxy G    WHERE   (pp.dered_r-pp.dered_i) < # AND   pp.cmodelmag_i-pp.extinction_i BETWEEN #    AND #    AND   (pp.dered_r-pp.dered_i) - (pp.dered_g-pp.dered_r)/#. > #    AND   pp.fiber2mag_i < # AND pp.devrad_i < #.    AND   pp.dered_i < # + #*((pp.dered_r-pp.dered_i) - (pp.dered_g-pp.dered_r)/#. - #)     AND S.z > #
